title: Title better not be too long. 256 code points max.
description:
This can be a very very very long description.
Definitly not more than 2048 Unicode code points however.

fields.name: How large can one be?
fields.value: The `name` can be 256 characters, the value can be `1024` characters.

fields.name: How many can I have in one embed?
What else should I know?
fields.value: You can inline the fields to make them show up next to each other if they fit.

fields.name: How large can the whole embed be?
fields.value: If you sum all characters in there from any property, 6000 is the max.
